Sous vide salmon is a culinary technique that involves cooking salmon (or any other food) in a water bath that is kept at a precise and constant temperature. This method results in perfectly cooked salmon that is moist, tender, and flavourful. Making this dish in an airfryer is a hassle-free and foolproof way to prepare this delicate fish, and this method is becoming increasingly popular among home cooks and professional chefs alike. Recipe by Instant Pot. Brine: Seasoning: 